parameters.Off: Turn off voice reverb, that is, to use the original voice.

parameters.FX_KTV: The reverb style typical of a KTV venue (enhanced).

parameters.FX_VOCAL_CONCERT: The reverb style typical of a concert hall (enhanced).

parameters.FX_SISTER: The reverb style typical of a young woman's voice.

parameters.FX_STUDIO: The reverb style typical of a recording studio (enhanced).

parameters.FX_POPULAR: The reverb style typical of popular music (enhanced).

parameters.FX_RNB: The reverb style typical of R&B music (enhanced).

parameters.FX_PHONOGRAPH: The voice effect typical of a vintage phonograph.

parameters.VIRTUAL_STEREO: The reverberation of the virtual stereo. The virtual stereo is an effect that renders the monophonic audio as the stereo audio, so that all users in the channel can hear the stereo voice effect.
